  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/23renlund,Elder Dale G. Renlund,48,"See Russell M. Nelson, “Overcome the World and Find Rest,” 96;Doctrine and Covenants 84:20. Notably, President Nelson said, “Each time you seek for and follow the promptings of the Spirit, each time you do anything good—things that ‘the natural man’ would not do—you are overcoming the world” (“Overcome the World and Find Rest,” 97)."
