  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/26christensen,Elder Craig C. Christensen,57,"3 Nephi 27:30–31. Three of the Savior’s Nephite disciples desired to remain in mortality with the sole purpose of bringing souls to Him. To these loyal disciples, Jesus said, “For this cause ye shall have fulness of joy; and ye shall sit down in the kingdom of my Father; yea, your joy shall be full, even as the Father hath given me fulness of joy; and ye shall be even as I am” (3 Nephi 28:10)."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/26christensen,Elder Craig C. Christensen,58,"Moses 1:39."
