  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/31bragg,Elder Mark A. Bragg,38,"Doctrine and Covenants 43:34; see also James E. Faust, “The Dignity of Self,”Ensign, May 1981, 10: “The dignity of self is greatly enhanced by looking upward in the search for holiness. Like the giant trees, we should reach up for the light. The most important source of light we can come to know is the gift of the Holy Ghost. It is the source of inner strength and peace.”"
