  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/45andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,42,"Alma 36:18. The other time “caught hold” is used in the Book of Mormon is speaking of those who “caught hold of the end of the rod of iron” (1 Nephi 8:24, 30)."
