  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,4,"We believe in Christ. As members of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, we worship Him and follow His teachings in the scriptures."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,5,"Before the Fall, our Heavenly Father spoke directly to Adam and Eve. Thereafter, the Father introduced His Only Begotten Son, Jesus Christ, as our Savior and Redeemer and gave us the command to “hear Him.”From this direction we conclude that the scriptural records of words spoken by “God” or the “Lord” are almost always the words of Jehovah, our risen Lord, Jesus Christ."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,6,"We are given the scriptures to direct our lives. As the prophet Nephi taught us, we should “feast upon the words of Christ; for behold, the words of Christ will tell you all things what ye should do.”Most of the scriptures reporting Jesus’s mortal ministries are descriptions of what Hedid. My message today consists of a selection of the words of our Savior—what Hesaid. These are words recorded in the New Testament (including the inspired additions of Joseph Smith) and in the Book of Mormon. Most of these selections are in the sequence in which our Savior spoke them."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,7,"“Verily, verily, I say unto thee, Except a man be born of water and of the Spirit, he cannot enter into the kingdom of God.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,8,"“Blessed are … they [which] do hunger and thirst after righteousness, for they shall be filledwith the Holy Ghost.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,9,"“Blessed are the peacemakers: for they shall be called the children of God.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,10,"“Ye have heard that it was said by them of old time, Thou shalt not commit adultery:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,11,"“But I say unto you, That whosoever looketh on a woman to lust after her hath committed adultery with her already in his heart.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,12,"“Ye have heard that it hath been said, Thou shalt love thy neighbour, and hate thine enemy."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,13,"“But I say unto you, Love your enemies, bless them that curse you, do good to them that hate you, and pray for them which despitefully use you, and persecute you;"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,14,"“That ye may be the children of your Father which is in heaven: for he maketh his sun to rise on the evil and on the good, and sendeth rain on the just and on the unjust.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,15,"“If ye forgive men their trespasses, your heavenly Father will also forgive you:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,16,"“But if ye forgive not men their trespasses, neither will your Father forgive your trespasses.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,17,"“If ye were of the world, the world would love his own: but because ye are not of the world, but I have chosen you out of the world, therefore the world hateth you.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,18,"“Wherefore, seek not the things of this world but seek ye first to build up the kingdom of God, and to establish his righteousness, and all these things shall be added unto you.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,19,"“Therefore all things whatsoever ye would that men should do to you, do ye even so to them: for this is the law and the prophets.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,20,"“Beware of false prophets, which come to you in sheep’s clothing, but inwardly they are ravening wolves."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,21,"“Ye shall know them by their fruits. Do men gather grapes of thorns, or figs of thistles?"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,22,“Even so every good tree bringeth forth good fruit; but a corrupt treebringeth forth evil fruit.”
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,23,"“Not every one that saith unto me, Lord, Lord, shall enter into the kingdom of heaven; but he that doeth the will of my Father which is in heaven.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,24,"“Come unto me, all ye that labour and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,25,"“Take my yoke upon you, and learn of me; for I am meek and lowly in heart: and ye shall find rest unto your souls."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,26,"“For my yoke is easy, and my burden is light.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,27,"“If any man will come after me, let him deny himself, and take up his cross and follow me."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,28,"“And now for a man to take up his cross, is to deny himself all ungodliness, and every worldly lust, and keep my commandments.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,29,"“Therefore, forsake the world, and save your souls; for what is a man profited, if he shall gain the whole world, and lose his own soul? Or what shall a man give in exchange for his soul?”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,30,"“If any man will do his will, he shall know of the doctrine, whether it be of God, or whether I speak of myself.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,31,"“And I say unto you, Ask, and it shall be given you; seek, and ye shall find; knock, and it shall be opened unto you."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,32,“For every one that asketh receiveth; and he that seeketh findeth; and to him that knocketh it shall be opened.”
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,33,"“Other sheep I have, which are not of this fold: them also I must bring, and they shall hear my voice; and there shall be one fold, and one shepherd.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,34,"“Jesus said unto her, I am the resurrection, and the life: he that believeth in me, though he were dead, yet shall he live:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,35,“And whosoever liveth and believeth in me shall never die.”
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,36,"“[The great commandment in the law is this:] Thou shalt love the Lord thy God with all thy heart, and with all thy soul, and with all thy mind."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,37,“This is the first and great commandment.
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,38,"“And the second is like unto it, Thou shalt love thy neighbour as thyself."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,39,“On these two commandments hang all the law and the prophets.”
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,40,"“He that hath my commandments, and keepeth them, he it is that loveth me: and he that loveth me shall be loved of my Father, and I will love him, and will manifest myself to him.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,41,"“Peace I leave with you, my peace I give unto you: not as the world giveth, give I unto you. Let not your heart be troubled, neither let it be afraid.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,42,"“This is my commandment, That ye love one another, as I have loved you.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,43,"“Behold my hands and my feet, that it is I myself: handle me, and see; for a spirit hath not flesh and bones, as ye see me have.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,44,"“Go ye therefore, and teach all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,45,"“Teaching them to observe all things whatsoever I have commanded you: and, lo, I am with you alway, even unto the end of the world.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,46,"After His ministry in the Holy Land, Jesus Christ appeared to therighteous on the American continent. These are some of the words He spoke there:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,47,"“Behold, I am Jesus Christ the Son of God. I created the heavens and the earth, and all things that in them are. I was with the Father from the beginning. I am in the Father, and the Father in me; and in me hath the Father glorified his name.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,48,"“I am the light and the life of the world. I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the end."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,49,"“And ye shall offer up unto me no more the shedding of blood; yea, your sacrifices and your burnt offerings shall be done away, for I will accept none of your sacrifices and your burnt offerings."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,50,"“And ye shall offer for a sacrifice unto me a broken heart and a contrite spirit. And whoso cometh unto me with a broken heart and a contrite spirit, him will I baptize with fire and with the Holy Ghost. …"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,51,"“Behold, I have come unto the world to bring redemption unto the world, to save the world from sin.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,52,"“And again I say unto you, ye must repent, and be baptized in my name, and become as a little child, or ye can in nowise inherit the kingdom of God.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,53,"“Therefore I would that ye should beperfecteven as I, or your Father who is in heaven is perfect.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,54,"“Verily, verily, I say unto you, ye must watch andprayalways, lest ye be tempted by the devil, and ye be led away captive by him.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,55,“Therefore ye must always pray unto the Father in my name.”
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,56,"“Therefore, whatsoever ye shall do, ye shall do it in my name; therefore ye shall call the church in my name.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,57,"“Behold I have given unto you my gospel, and this is the gospel which I have given unto you—that I came into the world to do the will of my Father, because my Father sent me."
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,58,"“And my Father sent me that I might be lifted up upon the cross; and after that I had been lifted up upon the cross, that I might draw all men unto me … to be judged of their works, whether they be good or whether they be evil.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,59,"“Now this is the commandment: Repent, all ye ends of the earth, and come unto me and be baptized in my name, that ye may be sanctified by the reception of the Holy Ghost, that ye may stand spotless before me at the last day.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,60,"We believe in Christ. I concludewith what He said about how we should know and follow His teachings:"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,61,"“But the Comforter, which is the Holy Ghost, whom the Father will send in my name, he shall teach you all things, and bring all things to your remembrance, whatsoever I have said unto you.”"
  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/51oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,62,"I affirm the truth of these teachings in the name of Jesus Christ, amen."
