  2023,"04",/general-conference/2023/04/56corbitt,Elder Ahmad S. Corbitt,22,"SeeJeremiah 1:4–5;Doctrine and Covenants 138:55–56;Abraham 3:22–23, 26; Guide to the Scriptures, “Premortal Life,” scriptures.ChurchofJesusChrist.org; “Lesson 2: The Plan of Salvation,”Preach My Gospel: A Guide to Missionary Service(2019), 48."
